{"tid":2203310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【港版國安法】憂引用「危及國家安全」條文任意拘留 英國更新對中國旅遊警示","createTime":"2020-09-15T08:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T09:21:01.000Z","uid":239336,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c16b975af07e179df08b462809ae386171d2e7ad","tid":2203310,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"英國更新對中國的旅遊警示，警告國民有被任意拘留的風險。「中國當局在部份情況下引用『危及國家安全』條文拘留外國人」，過往英國的警示未有提及有關任意拘留的風險，但英國外交部在網頁上的更新寫道：「包括英國國民在內有任意拘留的風險。」<br />\n<br />\n英國駐北京大使館發言人指，有關指示更新後，以便「清楚、真實地反映最近事件&hellip;&hellip;但我們的警示級別未有改變」。最近發生加拿大人、澳洲人、日本人及至少一名美國人在中國被當局以國家安全指控拘留，當中包括華裔澳洲籍記者成蕾，她8月中在北京被拘留，觸發中澳關係緊張。<br />\n<br />\n另外美國則提升香港警示級別，國務院指出因應武肺疫情與「任意執法」情況，國民到港前須三思。國務院在其網站提到，港版國安法7月1日生效之後，中國單方面任意在港行使警察與治安權，顯示其意圖運用權力針對「其所謂的『分裂國家』行為、顛覆、恐怖主義、『勾結』外國勢力」等廣泛活動，又指新法涵蓋非香港居民及香港以外機構的罪行，令公開批評中國的美國公民被捕、驅逐、起訴的風險增加，並指中國的「維護國家安全公署已在港運作」。網站提到中國發動「文宣」，誣捏一些人挑起社會動盪，某些情況下更公開他們的個人資料，令他們在社交網站受到恐嚇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200915/XVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200915%2FXVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=71967edb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200915%2FXVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y%2F&h=6b9bbfae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200915/XVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y/</a>"},{"pid":"a7f6d0106295882701cd9332a5de739c2dd4582a","tid":2203310,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1b488c84ea5579cb71f832ba026da9836852a4","tid":2203310,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ebd235d333feac4bd1965513c2909925f7d550","tid":2203310,"uid":33292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"英國已犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa87562459dc2c1e29d16b182b177014d25ca25","tid":2203310,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812623305c4614519292ecb483d169e2667f8f32","tid":2203310,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"任意執法呢樣野真係打中西方國家要害，李桂華立下大功"},{"pid":"fce02bef5047075a69837fc45f98f8e30d40b1dd","tid":2203310,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e704759d2f42b672a5dbe12444023c8a2d6556","tid":2203310,"uid":296830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">6章66條魔鬼👹惡魔法，魔鬼盡在細節中！外國人入境要小心睇路</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb7d5c689a9ccf9c3b2debc44ff65895c5a48a9","tid":2203310,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"812623305c4614519292ecb483d169e2667f8f32","tid":2203310,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"任意執法呢樣野真係打中西方國家要害，李桂華立下大功"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"Circus團長, 好阿叻"},{"pid":"bf7f2de0adb6bd3aeb21